{
  "texts": [
    "Subsequently, the Engineer implements the specified classes and functions as outlined in the design.",
    "Finally, the Quality Assurance Engineer creates and executes test cases to ensure rigorous code quality standards are met.",
    "These approaches emphasize a linear and sequential design process, ensuring structured progression and clear accountability at each stage.AgileCoder [101] and AgileGen [163] adopt Agile process models for software development, emphasizing iterative development by breaking complex tasks into small, manageable increments.",
    "AgileCoder [101] assigns Agile roles such as Product Manager and Scrum Master to facilitate sprintbased collaboration and development cycles.",
    "AgileGen enhances Agile practices with human-AI collaboration, integrating close user involvement to ensure alignment between requirements and generated code."
  ]
}